org.rsna.ctp.stdstages.anonymizer

Class AnonymizerStatus

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.rsna.ctp.stdstages.anonymizer.AnonymizerStatus

  • public class AnonymizerStatus
extends java.lang.Object
    A class to encapsulate typesafe enum return status values for CTP services. This class provides static final instances for each of the possible operational results (OK, SKIP, QUARANTINE).
